persons:
    person-tattered-prince:
        properties:
            gender: male
            name:
                value: "The Tattered Prince"
            title:
                - value: "Captain of the Windblown"
        notes: "A former nobleman of the Free City of Pentos, captain and founder of the Windblown, two thousand horse and foot, sworn to Yunkai. His right hand is Caggo (Corpsekiller), his left hand is Denzo D'Han the warrior bard (ADWD Appendix). Real name not given in this chunk. Silver-grey hair; pouches under his eyes described as large as saddlebags. His distinctive tattered cloak inspires fear in foes and emboldens his troops. He meets secretly with Quentyn Martell at the Purple Lotus inn in Meereen's old spice market quarter. Pretty Meris and Caggo Corpsekiller attend the meeting. He agrees to help steal a dragon in exchange for the city of Pentos — his true homeland. (ADWD 'The Spurned Suitor')"
